Description: Gaming Innovation Group Inc. (GiG) is an iGaming technology company. The Company is engaged in providing solutions, products and services to iGaming Operators. The Companyâ€™s principal activities include the provision of online gaming services, primarily remote gaming platforms, sportsbook and affiliate marketing operations. It offers cloud-based services and performance marketing through their business-to-business (B2B) solutions. The Company operates through two segments: affiliate marketing (Media) and platform and sportsbook services (Platform). Its Media segment is engaged in media affiliate business and helps grow its partners iGaming business by generating qualified leads through its digital marketing channels including search engine marketing (SEM)/PPC and SoMe. Its Platform segment includes technical iGaming platforms, front end development and other managed services, such as player safety, customer operations and customer relationship management (CRM)/marketing.
